{"root":{"data":{"text":"微波光子成像干扰一体化技术研究"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp0tfqfn4s","created":1531797858298,"text":"研究背景和意义","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp15m8zmog","created":1531797884814,"text":"研究背景","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy3hxxpm2o","created":1773129915403,"text":"军用领域"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxqhw1j94w","created":1773128896555,"text":"现代战争中，无人机的广泛应用给雷达探测带来了新的挑战。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxvi6n2v40","created":1773129289016,"text":"无人机的雷达散射截面积远远小于舰船坦克等，大大提高了雷达识别无人机的难度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyxvulti29s","created":1773129316056,"text":"无人机往往数量繁多，还采用集群技术协同作战，如果想要精准探测不同的无人机，这就对于雷达分辨率提出了很高的要求。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyxwh0757gg","created":1773129364814,"text":"雷达作为敌方攻击的重要目标，也需要具有一定的自保能力。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy4ppgombk","created":1773130010669,"text":"现代战场上敌方往往采用无人机饱和攻击消耗拦截系统的弹药，然后在空窗期发射导弹摧毁雷达。如果能识别干扰无人机只针对导弹进行拦截，就可以显著降低拦截系统的压力"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy3fxmim0w","created":1773129911031,"text":"民用领域"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy3qzuyhog","created":1773129935111,"text":"无人机黑飞问题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyybfuxms5c","created":1773130537782,"text":"无人机由于体型较小、可以低空起飞等原因，其监管存在较大难度。近些年来常常发生无人机在未经申请和授权的情况下黑飞进入机场或重要设施建筑的，不仅可能造成重大公共安全隐患，还可能导致重要信息泄漏。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy3w6xqj9c","created":1773129946423,"text":"无人机反制"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyybqxylzpc","created":1773130561909,"text":"因此需要既能够对无人机进行精准探测，又能够对其进行有效干扰的探测干扰一体化系统，从而实现有效的无人机反制。"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16beu2w4","created":1531797886335,"text":"存在的问题","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy1vdqfmdc","created":1773129787928,"text":"电域"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxrcuisruo","created":1773128963943,"text":"得益于集成电路和相控阵的发展等，传统电域探测干扰一体化程度高，但是由于电子瓶颈的限制，其难以实现高频宽带信号的高保真储存和高响应速度"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy1u22k2yo","created":1773129785046,"text":"微波光子"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy2myyd6v4","created":1773129847985,"text":"基于微波光子技术我们可以同时实现高频宽带信号的高保真存储和高响应速度，然而其一体化程度较低，多只承担单一探测或干扰功能。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16p7fl4o","created":1531797887169,"text":"微波光子技术的优势","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxuynlbq4g","created":1773129246506,"text":"能够实现高分辨率雷达成像","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy00vufzls","created":1773129643179,"text":"微波光子技术由于同时具有光子技术大带宽、抗电磁干扰的特性和微波技术灵活易操控的特性，因而能够实现传统雷达复杂甚至难以实现的宽带微波信号处理与传输，极大提高了雷达系统的距离分辨率，带来了雷达体制新的变革。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy11p18wsg","created":1773129723308,"text":"能够实现高频宽带的干扰"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy6aooksg0","created":1773130134699,"text":"基于微波光子技术的干扰信号产生能够解决数字射频存储器由于工作频段和瞬时带宽受限无法针对敌方雷达产生有效干扰的问题，有效提高雷达的生存能力。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy5viel2ps","created":1773130101668,"text":"成像干扰一体化带来的优势"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy6y000wzk","created":1773130185449,"text":"通过微波光子雷达成像干扰一体化设计，微波光子雷达探测得到的高分辨率成像结果可以用于判断敌方目标的位置、数量和类型等，从而可以根据不同情况选择不同的应对方式以应对复杂的战场环境"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0vi3wjs4","created":1531797862795,"text":"2. 阶段工作总结","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp17ohlswk","created":1531797889303,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18cjbegw","created":1531797890757,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18qmdhs8","created":1531797891608,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp28g7gco4","created":1531797969343,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0w7fnc0k","created":1531797864327,"text":"3. 亮点与不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":47,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp19f2yo84","created":1531797893087,"text":"1. 工作亮点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp19rtkeo8","created":1531797893858,"text":"2. 工作不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0wnpf808","created":1531797865311,"text":"4. 阶段工作规划","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1apwzq8k","created":1531797895919,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1b1h3z4g","created":1531797896618,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1bd2qds8","created":1531797897320,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1brn0xcs","created":1531797898200,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0xg6s1s0","created":1531797867033,"text":"5. 改进建议","layout_right_offset":{"x":61,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1ccip1s8","created":1531797899463,"text":"1. 对公司","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1d52ua04","created":1531797901190,"text":"2. 对部门","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-red-compat","version":"1.4.43"}